Personal information Victoria Azarenka

Victoria Fiodara≈≠na Azarenka is a Belarusian professional tennis player. Azarenka is a former world No. 1 in singles, having claimed the top ranking for the first time on 30 January 2012. She was the year-end No. 1 in 2012 and has held the top ranking for a combined total of 51 weeks.

This summary is provided by Wikipedia
